---
title: Parallel Implementation Lifecycle
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant A1 as Agent 1<br/>(wp-backend)
    participant A2 as Agent 2<br/>(wp-frontend)
    participant W1 as Worktree 1
    participant W2 as Worktree 2

    Note over O,W2: Phase A: Feature-Level Preflight
    O->>C: register_session(orchestrator)
    O->>C: submit_work(wp-contracts, priority=1)
    O->>C: submit_work(wp-backend, depends_on=[contracts])
    O->>C: submit_work(wp-frontend, depends_on=[contracts])

    Note over O,W2: Phase B: DAG-Scheduled Package Execution
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over A1,A2: wp-contracts completes first (no deps)
        A1->>C: get_work → wp-contracts
        A1->>C: acquire_lock(contract:openapi/v1.yaml)
        A1->>W1: generate OpenAPI spec + types
        A1->>C: complete_work(result={openapi_path, types})
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over A1,A2: wp-backend + wp-frontend run in PARALLEL
        par Backend Agent
            A1->>C: get_work → wp-backend
            A1->>C: acquire_lock(src/api/*, db:schema:*)
            A1->>C: get_task(wp-contracts) → read dep result
            A1->>W1: implement backend endpoints
            A1->>A1: scope check (git diff vs write_allow)
            A1->>A1: run verification tests
            A1->>C: complete_work(result={files, evidence})
        and Frontend Agent
            A2->>C: get_work → wp-frontend
            A2->>C: acquire_lock(src/ui/*)
            A2->>C: get_task(wp-contracts) → read dep result
            A2->>W2: implement UI components
            A2->>A2: scope check + verification
            A2->>C: complete_work(result={files, evidence})
        end
    end

    Note over O,W2: Phase C: Integration & Review
    O->>O: merge worktrees → integration branch
    O->>O: run full test suite
    O->>O: cross-package verification
    O->>C: submit to merge queue
